Authority:

 Secs. 201, 402, 403, 406, 409, 701, 704, 721, 
801 of the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act (21 U.S.C. 321, 
342, 343, 346, 348, 371, 374, 379e, 381); secs. 301, 307, 361, 
